    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The arrangement and layout of spaces inside architectural structures or parts of structures that are the result of conscious construction, are of practical use, are relatively stable and permanent. The term typically excludes the moveable works located within the space, such as furniture or accessories.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
